PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2023-00392023-01-31FIN
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Canada Development Investment Corporation to Incorporate a Subsidiary
PrecisOrder authorizing the Canada Development Investment Corporation to (1) procure the incorporation of a wholly-owned subsidiary that is yet to be named, all the shares of which, on incorporation, are to be held by, on behalf of or in trust for the Canada Development Investment Corporation; and (2) sell or otherwise dispose of any shares of the subsidiary.
